percent of an active judges caseload 
but they also agreed at the judges request to submit a bill 
calling for the general 30 percent raise and annual costofliving 
increases 
president bush has proposed a 25 percent increase along with a 
ban on speaking fees and a limit on outside earned income the 
judges oppose both the ban and the limit 
